HEADWORD: Directer
<hw>Di*rect"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who directs; a
director.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Directer plane</b></col> <fld>(Geom.)</fld>, <cd>the
